    "answer": "D",
    "solution": "$\\frac{1}{(2k-1)(2k+1)} = \\frac{1}{2}\\left(\\frac{1}{2k-1} - \\frac{1}{2k+1}\\right)$. Телескоп: $\\frac{1}{2}\\left(1 - \\frac{1}{2017}\\right) = \\frac{1}{2} \\cdot \\frac{2016}{2017} = \\frac{1008}{2017}$."
